{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadio","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash",